com.centurylink.mdw.cli

Class Import

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.centurylink.mdw.cli.Setup
      • com.centurylink.mdw.cli.Import
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Operation

    public class Import
extends Setup
    Imports asset packages from Git or Maven. If --group-id option is specified, imports from Maven; otherwise, if --packageName is specified imports from an mdw instance; otherwise, imports from associated Git repository. Note: this performs a Git HARD RESET only if --hard-reset is specified, overwriting all local changes.
